-06-23T01:52:10.946Z","version":1},{"id":"lr_con3","type":"text","x":815,"y":620,"text":"✗ More complex to implement correctly","fontSize":12,"fontFamily":2,"createdAt":"2026-06-23T01:52:10.946Z","updatedAt":"2026-06-23T01:52:10.946Z","version":1}]}
